The paper deals with multimedia retrieval using cross-modal hashing, which involves computer vision (CV) and information retrieval (IR) techniques. The proposed approach uses a hybrid deep architecture, which suggests the involvement of machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, and cs.AI.
